early on [[BBC iPlayer]] as of 23 March.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.goodhousekeeping.com/uk/lifestyle/a31892161/bbc-malory-towers-adaption-iplayer/|title=BBC's new Malory Towers adaption arrives on iPlayer early|journal=Good Housekeeping|first=Elena|last=Chabo|date=23 March 2020|accessdate=23 March 2020}}</ref> The Canada release date is yet to be announced.\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n*{{IMDb title|11129816}}\n\n[[Category:2020 British television series debuts]]\n[[Category:2020s British children's television series]]\n[[Category:2020s Canadian children's television series]]\n[[Category:BBC children's television programmes]]\n[[Category:British television programmes based on children's books]]\n[[Category:Canadian television programs based on children's books]]\n[[Category:English-language television programs]]\n", "name_user": "Ripironman", "label": "safe", "comment": "added a series option as company that co produce it say they hope to do season 2", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Malory_Towers_(TV_series)"}
